data.title: For Caturday, here's some cats I painted on my sketchbook over the last week.

images.description: When I'm struggling with art block, I go on the r/cats subreddit, usually under the "Mourning/Loss" flair and paint the cats that are posted there to honour their memory.
From a stranger who loves cats to another who loved and lost one, I see you and you are not alone.

The one on the left was not under the "Mourning/Loss" flair but her eyes were just so beautiful I had to paint it!

You can see more of my work on my instagram at: https://www.instagram.com/kat.t.illustrations/
